        <p>The conference is run by Helle Martens’ tiny indie business team, and fueled by a strong passion for the field of UX and design.</p>
        <p>We look forward to welcoming you to one of the world’s greatest communities, and two days filled with superb content, inspiration, networking, new knowledge, and new insights.</p>
